{"tid":2434940,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"McAfee創辦人因吹捧投資虛擬貨幣而獲利1300萬美元 遭起訴詐欺洗錢","createTime":"2021-03-06T00:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T09:43:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"770e8f88ea5c58622d9dd4bba22ea0c6e8cded25","tid":2434940,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:46:25.000Z","msg":"知名電腦防毒軟體McAfee創辦人約翰邁克菲（John McAfee）又惹上官司！因逃漏稅而被美國追緝的他，因涉嫌為私利吹捧加密貨幣，而遭美國檢方起訴詐欺及串謀洗錢罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據紐約曼哈頓聯邦法院文件，現年75歲的邁克菲和其加密貨幣（cryptocurrency）投資夥伴小華森（Jimmy Gale Watson Jr.）被共同起訴詐欺及串謀洗錢罪。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官史特勞斯（Audrey Strauss）透過聲明表示，邁克菲和小華森於2017及2018年間，透過社群網站平台吹捧加密貨幣，並謊稱因此獲利超過1300萬美元（約3億6326萬元台幣）。史特勞斯說：「被告利用邁克菲的推特帳號，向成千上萬的追隨者吹捧不同的加密貨幣，透過虛假誤導言論達成他們追求自我利益的真正目的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210306/NF5H7BFXBBHIRKAD2MLETN3QMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210306%2FNF5H7BFXBBHIRKAD2MLETN3QMM%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=686e6e82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210306%2FNF5H7BFXBBHIRKAD2MLETN3QMM%2F&h=e44bf028\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210306/NF5H7BFXBBHIRKAD2MLETN3QMM/</a>"},{"pid":"1cf1b58c5b3a4e3123c20c2c52b2e60f883ee311","tid":2434940,"uid":3967,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:49:27.000Z","msg":"tsla 老細呢?"},{"pid":"26e0824ed4b342c47d1bc051452c727fe327f0ef","tid":2434940,"uid":67208,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:49:39.000Z","msg":"elon musk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2054792e0f6245be50e41f95fed538f27b3f2ae","tid":2434940,"uid":110988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"美國有公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/